{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":5000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"What you just heard"},{"time":26000,"text":"are the interactions of barometric pressure, wind and temperature readings"},{"time":29000,"text":"that were recorded of Hurricane Noel in 2007."},{"time":33000,"text":"The musicians played off a three-dimensional graph of weather data like this."},{"time":37000,"text":"Every single bead, every single colored band,"},{"time":39000,"text":"represents a weather element"},{"time":41000,"text":"that can also be read as a musical note."},{"time":44000,"text":"I find weather extremely fascinating."},{"time":46000,"text":"Weather is an amalgam of systems"},{"time":48000,"text":"that is inherently invisible to most of us."},{"time":50000,"text":"So I use sculpture and music"},{"time":52000,"text":"to make it, not just visible,"},{"time":54000,"text":"but also tactile and audible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56000,"text":"All of my work begins very simple."},{"time":58000,"text":"I extract information from a specific environment"},{"time":60000,"text":"using very low-tech data collecting devices --"},{"time":63000,"text":"generally anything I can find in the hardware store."},{"time":66000,"text":"I then compare my information to the things I find on the Internet --"},{"time":69000,"text":"satellite images, weather data"},{"time":71000,"text":"from weather stations as well as offshore buoys."},{"time":74000,"text":"That's both historical as well as real data."},{"time":76000,"text":"And then I compile all of these numbers on these clipboards that you see here."},{"time":79000,"text":"These clipboards are filled with numbers."},{"time":81000,"text":"And from all of these numbers,"},{"time":83000,"text":"I start with only two or three variables."},{"time":85000,"text":"That begins my translation process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87000,"text":"My translation medium is a very simple basket."},{"time":90000,"text":"A basket is made up of horizontal and vertical elements."},{"time":94000,"text":"When I assign values to the vertical and horizontal elements,"},{"time":97000,"text":"I can use the changes of those data points over time"},{"time":100000,"text":"to create the form."},{"time":102000,"text":"I use natural reed,"},{"time":104000,"text":"because natural reed has a lot of tension in it"},{"time":106000,"text":"that I cannot fully control."},{"time":108000,"text":"That means that it is the numbers that control the form,"},{"time":110000,"text":"not me."},{"time":112000,"text":"What I come up with are forms like these."},{"time":114000,"text":"These forms are completely made up"},{"time":116000,"text":"of weather data or science data."},{"time":118000,"text":"Every colored bead, every colored string,"},{"time":120000,"text":"represents a weather element."},{"time":122000,"text":"And together, these elements, not only construct the form,"},{"time":124000,"text":"but they also reveal behavioral relationships"},{"time":126000,"text":"that may not come across"},{"time":128000,"text":"through a two-dimensional graph."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"When you step closer, you actually see"},{"time":132000,"text":"that it is indeed all made up of numbers."},{"time":134000,"text":"The vertical elements"},{"time":136000,"text":"are assigned a specific hour of the day."},{"time":138000,"text":"So all the way around, you have a 24-hour timeline."},{"time":141000,"text":"But it's also used to assign a temperature range."},{"time":143000,"text":"On that grid, I can then weave the high tide readings,"},{"time":146000,"text":"water temperature, air temperature and Moon phases."},{"time":149000,"text":"I also translate weather data into musical scores."},{"time":152000,"text":"And musical notation allows me a more nuanced way"},{"time":155000,"text":"of translating information"},{"time":157000,"text":"without compromising it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":159000,"text":"So all of these scores are made up of weather data."},{"time":161000,"text":"Every single color, dot, every single line,"},{"time":163000,"text":"is a weather element."},{"time":165000,"text":"And together, these variables construct a score."},{"time":168000,"text":"I use these scores to collaborate with musicians."},{"time":170000,"text":"This is the 1913 Trio"},{"time":172000,"text":"performing one of my pieces"},{"time":174000,"text":"at the Milwaukee Art Museum."},{"time":176000,"text":"Meanwhile, I use these scores as blueprints"},{"time":179000,"text":"to translate into sculptural forms like this,"},{"time":183000,"text":"that function still in the sense"},{"time":185000,"text":"of being a three-dimensional weather visualization,"},{"time":187000,"text":"but now they're embedding"},{"time":189000,"text":"the visual matrix of the musical score,"},{"time":191000,"text":"so it can actually be read as a musical score."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"What I love about this work"},{"time":195000,"text":"is that it challenges our assumptions"},{"time":197000,"text":"of what kind of visual vocabulary belongs in the world of art, versus science."},{"time":200000,"text":"This piece here is read very differently"},{"time":202000,"text":"depending on where you place it."},{"time":204000,"text":"You place it in an art museum, it becomes a sculpture."},{"time":206000,"text":"You place it in a science museum,"},{"time":208000,"text":"it becomes a three-dimensional visualization of data."},{"time":211000,"text":"You place it in a music hall,"},{"time":213000,"text":"it all of a sudden becomes a musical score."},{"time":215000,"text":"And I really like that,"},{"time":217000,"text":"because the viewer is really challenged"},{"time":219000,"text":"as to what visual language"},{"time":221000,"text":"is part of science versus art versus music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"The other reason why I really like this"},{"time":225000,"text":"is because it offers an alternative entry point"},{"time":228000,"text":"into the complexity of science."},{"time":230000,"text":"And not everyone has a Ph.D. in science."},{"time":232000,"text":"So for me, that was my way into it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}